======== REACT JS =========
mkdir bookworm
cd bookworm
npx create-react-app bookworm-react
cd bookworm-react 
code .
create .eslintrc file

To create Route ==> npm add react-route
npm add react-router-dom

INSTALL SEMANTIC UI
npm add semantic-ui-react semantic-ui-css

After installation, Goto index.js and import this to it
import "semantic-ui-css/semantic.min.css";

email validator ==> npm add validator

npm add prop-types

ADD REDUX
npm add redux react-redux redux-thunk
AFTER SUCCESSFUL INSTALLATION IMPORT THE FOLLOWING TO THE INDEX.JS
import { createStore, applyMiddleware } from 'redux';
import { Provider } from 'react-redux';
import thunk from 'redux-thunk';

npm add --dev redux-devtools-extension
